{
  "stem": "71.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took the other group away, and they told-- they kept us maybe half a night in the cold outside.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after that, they told us to go back in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the other-- the other group they took away and we never heard from them since.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they put us on trains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The next day, I went to get water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They needed somebody to bring water, and I was the first one so I can wash my face.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my sisters came running, saying, the train is going already away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're taking us away from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From Auschwitz, we are going to a-- to a [INAUDIBLE] camp, to a working place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I-- I would not give up the pail of water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I ran with the pail of water, spilling half of it so to have a little bit of water.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a girl with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took her to another train where-- and she was all alone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went over to German, and I said-- you know, I speak German-- so I said to him, there's a girl here that is all alone, and can we exchange somebody else and have her with us?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- you know, we adopted her as the forth sister and she was with us, you know, till we were liberated and we came to-- to Landsberg [?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Foundation ?] and she left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the guard allowed it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They allowed it because I said that she's like-- she's all alone, and she's young.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she's a good worker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so to them, it didn't make any difference.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, there were-- there were [INAUDIBLE] them.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
